  \column{.30}
  \block{Control}{
    \Large
    We would like to toggle the state of the network between the "epileptic" regime and the standard power law behavior seen in the rat cortex culture.
    
    \vspace{1cm}
    
    There are three different approaches that can be taken:

    \begin{itemize}

    \item Increase or decrease noise globally.
    \item Change local field at individual neurons.
    \item "Prune" neuron connections.
    \end{itemize}

